## 6. GROUP BY extensions
```sql
-- Subtotals + grand total in one query (great for BI-style reports)
SELECT country, product_category, SUM(revenue)
FROM sales
GROUP BY ROLLUP (country, product_category);

-- All combinations of subtotals
SELECT country, product_category, SUM(revenue)
FROM sales
GROUP BY CUBE (country, product_category);

-- Specific custom groupings
SELECT country, product_category, SUM(revenue)
FROM sales
GROUP BY GROUPING SETS ((country), (product_category), ());
```

